-- Brightstar Names Former AMD Finance Chief Thomas Seifert as CFO
-- B y   L i s a   R a p a p o r t
-- 2012-11-29T15:15:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-29/brightstar-names-former-amd-finance-chief-thomas-seifert-as-cfo.html
Brightstar Corp. has hired former
 Advanced Micro Devices Inc. (AMD)  executive Thomas Seifert as chief
financial officer replacing Dennis Strand, who will lead a new
business unit.  Seifert will start Dec. 1, Miami-based Brightstar said
today in a statement. AMD, the second-largest maker of
processors for personal computers, said in September that
Seifert was leaving his post as CFO to pursue other
opportunities.  Strand has been named president of Brightstar Financial
Services, the company said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lisa Rapaport in  New York  at 
 lrapaport1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
